Files under debian/:
--------------------
This package was debianized by Jason Tan <jtan325@gmail.com>.

The Debian package was maintained by Bartosz Fenski <fenio@debian.org>
from version 1.4.1-1 to 1.4.4-1.

The Debian package is currently maintained by
Kapil Hari Paranjape <kapil@debian.org>

Some modifications were made by Steve Langasek <vorlon@debian.org>
and Laszlo Boszormenyi (GCS) <gcs@debian.hu>.

The files under debian/ constitute source for the Debian packaging.
Each such file should be deemed to carry a notice as follows:

